{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/mxschmitt/awesome-playwright/readme","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"322f03a6-41d2-550f-aa90-e42fd08c4497","html":"<h1 id=\"awesome-playwright-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-playwright-awesome\" aria-label=\"awesome playwright awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome Playwright <a href=\"https://awesome.re\"><img src=\"https://awesome.re/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A curated list of awesome tools, utils and projects using Playwright</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/playwright\">Playwright</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/playwright\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">43.3k</span></span></a> is a Node.js library to automate Firefox, WebKit and Chromium based browsers via a single API.</p>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#integrations\">Integrations</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#language-support\">Language Support</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#utils\">Utils</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#reporters\">Reporters</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#showcases\">Showcases</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#guides\">Guides</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#contribute\">Contribute</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"integrations\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#integrations\" aria-label=\"integrations permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Integrations</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/playwright-community/jest-playwright/\">jest-playwright</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/playwright-community/jest-playwright/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">470</span></span></a> - Jest adapter for running Playwright.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Codeception/CodeceptJS\">CodeceptJS</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Codeception/CodeceptJS\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">3.8k</span></span></a> - Supercharged End 2 End Testing Framework for Node.js.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/alixaxel/chrome-aws-lambda#usage-with-playwright\">chrome-aws-lambda</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/alixaxel/chrome-aws-lambda#usage-with-playwright\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2.8k</span></span></a> - Support for running Microsoft's Playwright on AWS Lambda and Google Cloud Functions.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/playwright-github-action\">playwright-github-action</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/playwright-github-action\" style=\"text-