ht on a Heroku Dyno.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/abhinaba-ghosh/axe-playwright\">axe-playwright</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/abhinaba-ghosh/axe-playwright\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">103</span></span></a> - Custom commands for Playwright to run accessibility (a11y) checks with axe-core.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Widen/expect-axe-playwright\">expect-axe-playwright</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Widen/expect-axe-playwright\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">14</span></span></a> - Expect matchers to perform Axe accessibility tests in your Playwright tests.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Tallyb/cucumber-playwright\">cucumber-playwright</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Tallyb/cucumber-playwright\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;