hon\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">7k</span></span></a> - Official Playwright port to Python.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/playwright-dotnet\">playwright-dotnet</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/playwright-dotnet\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.6k</span></span></a> - Official Playwright port to .NET.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/playwright-java\">playwright-java</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/playwright-java\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">576</span></span></a> - Official Playwright port to Java.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mxschmitt/playwright-go\">playwright-go</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/mxschmitt/playwright-go\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">972</span></span></a> - Playwright port for Golang.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/YusukeIwaki/playwright-ruby-client\">playwright-ruby-client</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/YusukeIwaki/playwright-ruby-client\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">122</span></span></a> - Playwright port for Ruby.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/naqvis/playwright-cr\">playwright-cr</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/naqvis/playwright-cr\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">17</span></span></a> - Playwright port for Crystal.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/octaltree/playwright-rust\">playwright-rust</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/octaltree/playwright-rust\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">106</span></span></a> - Playwright port for Rust.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/teodesian/playwright-perl\">playwright-perl</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/teodesian/playwright-perl\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">18</span></span></a> - Playwright port for Perl.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"utils\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#utils\" aria-label=\"utils permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Utils</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://try.playwright.tech\">Try Playwright</a> - Interactive playground for running Playwright tests.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Georgegriff/query-selector-shadow-dom\">query-selector-shadow-dom</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Georgegriff/query-selector-shadow-dom\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">190</span></span></a> - Extend the selectors engine by selecting Shadow DOM roots.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/hdorgeval/playwright-fluent\">playwright-fluent</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/hdorgeval/playwright-fluent\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">90</span></span></a> - Fluent API Wrapper around Playwright.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://headlesstesting.com\">headless-testing</a> - Connect your Playwright tests with browsers in the Cloud.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/playwright-community/expect-playwright\">expect-playwright</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/playwright-community/expect-playwright\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;posit